text: Ursy is a municipality in the district of Glâne in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. == History == On 1 January 2001, the former municipalities of Vauderens, Bionnens and Mossel merged into the municipality of Ursy.Nomenklaturen – Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 4 April 2011 The former municipality of Vuarmarens merged on 1 January 2012 into the municipality of Ursy.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz published by the Swiss Federal Statistical Office accessed 17 February 2011 == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Municipalities in Glâne
